Predicting new values

In [ ]:
prediction = SVC_model.predict(np.array([[1, 51, 23000]]))

if prediction == 0.0:
    print("Eligible to buy a Hatchback.")
elif prediction == 1.0:
    print("Not eligible for buying a car.")
elif prediction == 2.0:
    print("Eligible to buy a SUV.")
else:
    print("Eligible to buy a Sedan.")

print(prediction)
